# Brand consistency

Before adding a **new component**, **new page section**, or **significant styling**, read [docs/BRAND-GUIDE.md](docs/BRAND-GUIDE.md).

- Prefer [components/cw/](components/cw/) and shadcn [components/ui/](components/ui/) with brand variants over bespoke markup.
- Use brand tokens from [app/brand-tokens.css](app/brand-tokens.css) — no ad-hoc hex colors in JSX or CSS.
- Primary actions use ink (`--primary` / `--ink`); Spark orange (`--spark`) is for accents and data emphasis.
- If you introduce a reusable UI pattern, add it to `components/cw/` and update `docs/BRAND-GUIDE.md` in the same change.
